s buffers)\nnxp_log_shutdown();\n```\n\n### Logging Calls\n```c\n// Direct logging (always compiled in)\nnxp_log_info(\"Connection established: id=%llu\", conn_id);\nnxp_log_error(\"Crypto failure: %s\", error_msg);\n\n// Conditional macros (compiled out if NXP_ENABLE_LOGGING=OFF)\nNXP_LOG_DEBUG(\"Stream %llu: wrote %zu bytes\", stream_id, bytes);\nNXP_LOG_WARN(\"Retransmitting packet %llu\", pkt_num);\n```\n\n### Integration with Flight Recorder\n```c\n// Error tracking automatically logs\nNXP_LOG_ERROR_ONLY(NXP_ERR_CRYPTO_FAIL, \"AEAD decrypt failed\");\n\n// Flight recorder dumps use logging\nnxp_flight_dump(50);  // Logs last 50 events\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Key Features\n\n### 1. **Asynchronous Logging**\n- Non-blocking writes\n- Background thread handles I/O\n- Minimal impact on hot path (~50ns overhead)\n\n### 2. **Structured Output**\n- Timestamp (microsecond precision)\n- Log level\n- Thread ID\n- File:line information\n- Formatted message\n\n### 3. **Conditional Compilation**\n```cmake\n# Enable logging\ncmake .. -DNXP_ENABLE_LOGGING=ON\n\n# Disable logging (zero overhead)\ncmake .. -DNXP_ENABLE_LOGGING=OFF\n```\n\n### 4. **Integration with Error Tracking**\n- Errors automatically logged\n- Flight recorder dumps logged\n- Error statistics available\n\n---\n\n## 📈 Performance\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Logging overhead | ~50ns per call |\n| Memory usage | ~1MB (Quill buffers) |\n| Thread safety | Yes (lock-free) |\n| Async I/O | Yes (background thread) |\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 Log Output Example\n\n```\n[2026-04-06 16:20:30.123456] [INFO] Connection created: scid_len=8 is_server=0\n[2026-04-06 16:20:30.123789] [DEBUG] Connection state: 0 -> 3\n[2026-04-06 16:20:30.124012] [DEBUG] Stream created: id=0 type=0\n[2026-04-06 16:20:30.124234] [TRACE] RTT updated: latest=25000 smoothed=25000 min=25000 var=12500\n[2026-04-06 16:20:30.124567] [ERROR] ERROR -8: cryptographic failure at connection.c:547 - AEAD decrypt failed\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Production Benef